Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Full Set of Amenities in Each Building
Each building has a fitness center, conference center, game room, tenant wi-fi lounge, full service deli with catering, parking deck, mother's room

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Situated in a campus-like setting on 29 acres with views of the Ned Brown Forest Preserve and Olympic Park.  Immediate tollway access to Route 53/290 and less than one mile from Woodfield Mall.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Class "A" building space with award winning design. Furnished spec suites for immediate occupancy. State of the art systems including raised floor HVAC system which enhances air quality, employee comfort, planning flexibility and energy cost efficiency. Two 5-level parking garages connected to buildings.  Duplicated amenities (within the complex) including conference centers, delis (with catering available), fitness centers, game rooms, wi-fi lounges, mothers’ rooms, etc. Outdoor tenant courtyard including pergolas, guest seating, and water feature. Unique full-height windows offer a plethora of natural light for increased productivity and higher employee satisfaction.  The property received the “Most Improved” Landscaping award in the Commercial Category for the recently completed landscape enhancements in our brand new courtyard and outdoor seating area.
